==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Maine
<hw>Maine</hw> <pr>(m⟦amac⟧n)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>One of the
New England States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Maine law</b></col>, <cd>any law prohibiting the
manufacture and sale of intoxicating beverages, esp. one resembling that
enacted in the State of Maine. At present, the state of Maine sells such
beverages in its own stores.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>maine lobster</ent>⟦br⟧
